name: Skill Evaluation Report
query:
SELECT
emp.`employee` AS "Employee Code:Link/Employee:100",
emp.`employee_name` AS "Employee Name:Data:100",
emp.`date_of_joining` AS "DoJ:Date:100",
emp.`line` AS "Line:Link/Line:100",
CASE
WHEN `tabAuto Cutting and Crimping`.`month_of_evaluation` != "" THEN  `tabAuto Cutting and Crimping`.`month_of_evaluation`
ELSE "-"
END AS "MoE::100"
FROM
`tabEmployee` emp
LEFT JOIN
`tabAuto Cutting and Crimping`
ON emp.`employee` = `tabAuto Cutting and Crimping`.`employee_code`
WHERE
emp.`status`='Active'
ORDER BY emp.`date_of_joining` ASC
